      ],
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "outError",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "On input, specify a pointer to an error object. If a lock cannot be acquired, this pointer contains an "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "NSError"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " object that describes the problem. You may specify "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "nil"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " for this property."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if a lock was acquired or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if it was not."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You must call this method before attempting to configure the hardware related properties of the device. This method returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when it successfully locks the device for configuration by your code. After configuring the device properties, call "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387917-unlockforconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to release the configuration lock and allow other apps to make changes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You may hold onto a lock (instead of releasing it) if you require the device properties to remain unchanged. However, holding the device lock unnecessarily may degrade capture quality in other apps sharing the device. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "In iOS, directly configuring a capture device’s "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1389221-activeformat"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " property changes the capture session’s preset to "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesessionpresetinputpriority"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". Upon making this change, the capture session no longer automatically configures the capture format when you call the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesession/1388185-startrunning"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " method or call the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesession/1388173-commitconfiguration"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " method after changing the session topology (that is, adding, removing, or rearranging capture inputs and outputs). In macOS, a capture session can still automatically configure the capture format after you make changes. To prevent automatic changes to the capture format in macOS, follow these steps:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "orderedList",
              "items": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Lock the device with the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387810-lockforconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Change the device’s "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1389221-activeformat"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " property."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Begin capture with the session’s "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesession/1388185-startrunning"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Unlock the device with the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387917-unlockforconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Or, to prevent automatic changes after modifying session topology in macOS:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "orderedList",
              "items": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Lock the device with the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": false,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387810-lockforconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Call the session’s "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesession/1389174-beginconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method, change topology, then call the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturesession/1388173-commitconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Unlock the device with the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "reference",
                          "isActive": true,
                          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1387917-unlockforconfiguration"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " method."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
